headline: Nick Dawkins Named 2024 Allstate Wuerffel Trophy Recipient and Allstate AFCA Good Works Team Captain
summary: NORTHBROOK, Ill., December 13, 2024--Nick Dawkins, a three-time Academic All-Big Ten honoree and Penn State's 2023 Public Service Award winner who founded the Dawkins Family Foundation to champion academic and athletic excellence for young students, is this year’s Allstate Wuerffel Trophy recipient and Allstate AFCA Good Works Team Captain.
